sources.title: Jesus of Nazareth (1916)
sources.description: This movie was filmed by Sydney Olcott in 1916 and is also known as "From the Manger to the Cross." More information on the film can be found here: http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0002199/ It was found on Youtube, and since it was filmed in 1916, it has long since gone into the public domain.
